text: James Craib (27 November 1917 - 19 December 1994) was an English cricketer. He played two first-class matches for Cambridge University Cricket Club in 1937. ==See also== * List of Cambridge University Cricket Club players ==References== ==External links== * Category:1917 births Category:1994 deaths Category:English cricketers Category:Cambridge University cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Kandy
